extendedInfo.description: The Choice Strategies Mobile app provides a single access point for participants to manage their consumer driven healthcare and other tax favored benefit accounts. The Choice Strategies Mobile app shares user authentication with the Choice Strategies Member Portal, meaning that registered users can merely download the application and log in using the same user ID and password to access the Choice Strategies Member Portal. The Choice Strategies mobile app includes Detailed Account Information such as account balances and recent transactions.

reviews.title: Best insurance app ever
reviews.comment: This app helps both choice and myself keep track of medical spending
reviews.author: Jack Neville

reviews.title: Broken
reviews.comment: Would have rated this higher if submitting a claim was not broken.  Receiving error messages \"Cannot contact server\" when trying to submit a claim over the span of 2 days.  [7/3/2013] Still broken.  Error is now internal server error.  Down graded to 1 star.
reviews.author: Conrad Hosang
